[00:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '[Music] Every photo you\'ve ever taken is flat, but reality isn\'t flat. Meet the camera that captures reality itself. This is Portal, the first true'

[00:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'spatial camera. It scans, sees every angle, and recreates worlds. Here\'s where it gets wild.'

[00:29] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Your vision now reality. Watch the streets unfold in 3D, complete with texture, lighting, and context.'

[00:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'We do shots test every angle on digital sets, all before day one. Then step into endless worlds. All from the same studio floor. Every'

[01:01] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'story, any location. The entire world becomes your stage. Here\'s your portal to infinite film sets.'

[01:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Why show a house when you can share a home? Grab your portal cam, take a walk, and watch the space come alive. Let clients imagine a life here'

[01:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'from anywhere. Your listings just became experiences. Share the world in one click. Distance'

[01:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'won\'t tamper with interest. Here\'s your portal to every dream home. Turn anywhere into your playground. Real locations become game worlds.'

[01:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Race through actual streets. Every corner of Earth is now playable. Here\'s your portal to limitless play.'

[02:07] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Some moments are too precious for photographs. They deserve to be preserved in full years later.'

[02:22] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Step back into that day. See the joy in each other\'s eyes. Feel the warmth exactly as it was. Share the'

[02:36] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'moments with the ones you love over and over again. Here\'s your portal to forever. Portal Cam, the first true spatial'

[02:48] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'camera. [Music]'
